727638f-a.title: Queens: Northern Boulevard - 245th Street
727638f-a.text:
Northern Boulevard, north side, at 245th Street, showing
the Douglaston Inn. It was known as the North Shore Hotel in
1873. Northern Boulevard, here, was then called the Floshing
and North Hempstead Turnpike.
P. L. Sperr  April 12, 1927
NO REPRODUCTIONS
